<term>2: </term> Pure translation
</para>
<para id="element-35">
For pure translation, we consider that the rotating disk is not rotating at all. Each particle of the disk is translating with linear velocity that of center of mass, "
<m:math>
<m:msub>
<m:mi> v </m:mi>
<m:mi> C </m:mi>
