</m:math>
". Unlike the case of pure rotation, each of the particle - whether situating on the rim or within the disk - is moving with same velocity. In the figure, we have shown the linear velocities of particles with appropriate vectors, occupying four positions on the rim. 
</para>
<para id="element-36">
